description.plain:
The mysterious dvsn (pronounced “division”) is an alternative R&B act based in Toronto, comprised of OVO producer Nineteen85 and R&B singer Daniel Daley.

Nineteen85 originally brought dvsn into the limelight when he played “The Line” and “With Me” on the eighth OVO Sound Radio tracklist in 2015.

It was initially unclear who was involved with dvsn, but Nineteen85 confirmed that he started the group “to explore some stuff that I normally wouldn’t get to do as this quote-unquote pop producer,” as well  as verifying that Daley was a part of the duo.

dvsn’s debut album, SEPT. 5TH, (originally set for April 1, 2016), was released on March 27, 2016, with the title referencing the release date of their first two singles.

In 2016, dvsn broke further into the public eye with an appearance on Drake’s fourth studio album, Views, where they appeared on “Faithful.”

On October 13, 2017 dvsn released their sophomore album Morning After.

On April 17, 2020, they released their third album, A Muse In Her Feelings, featuring artists like PARTYNEXTDOOR, Future, Popcaan, and more. The following year dvsn released Amusing Her Feelings, serving as a deluxe edition and featuring four new tracks.

songs.title: Hallucinations

description.plain:
“Hallucinations” are experiences involving the apparent perception of something not present.

In this song, Daniel Daley (the singer in the duo that is dvsn) has hallucinations of a girl he was with in a past relationship, and that he can’t get over. His lover is gone, but his dreams and hallucinations make him long for this significant other, hurting him emotionally in the process.

“Hallucinations” is the fourth single off of dvsn’s debut album, Sept. 5.

The official music video for “Hallucinations” was released on March 6, 2017.

songs.title: With Me

description.plain:
“With Me” details dvsn and his craving for a sexual relationship. All dvsn wants to do is hang out with their partner, wanting the significant other to “fuck with [them],” and have a good time with sex.

“With Me” is the first single from dvsn, and was  released on September 5, 2015 on their Soundcloud. The song would later become popular when it premiered on the eighth episode of OVO Sound Radio alongside their second single, “The Line”.

The production is handled by OVO producer Nineteen85, who is rumoured to be a part of dvsn.
